msg: Unchecked (Runtime) Exception AddedMEPContext added to the core. MEPContextFactory is added to provide for the extensibility of the different MEPs that might occure (like IN_IN_OUT may be) in the future. BasicMEPContext is the default MEPContext that is capable of handling IN_OUT and IN_ONLY MEPs. AxisOperation is made MEPContext aware. ..
